For ReviewersFor PR AuthorsFor Referencing Comments <p>Reviewers can request code changes by:</p> <ol> <li>Selecting the code block to be modified.</li> <li>Adding a comment with the syntax:</li> </ol> <pre><code>/implement &lt;code-change-description&gt;
</code></pre> <p></p> <p>PR authors can implement suggested changes by replying to a review comment using either:</p> <ol> <li>Add specific implementation details as described above</li> </ol> <pre><code>/implement &lt;code-change-description&gt;
</code></pre> <ol> <li>Use the original review comment as instructions</li> </ol> <pre><code>/implement
</code></pre> <p></p> <p>You can reference and implement changes from any comment by:</p> <pre><code>/implement &lt;link-to-an-inline-comment&gt;
</code></pre> <p></p> <p>Note that the implementation will occur within the review discussion thread.</p>
